Topic
Pub/Sub triggered Cloud Function connecting to Cloud SQL (public IP) with Secret Manager for credentials.
Objective
Build a complete serverless pipeline: Pub/Sub → Eventarc → Cloud Function → Cloud SQL, with secrets handled securely.
Key Concepts

Cloud SQL Auth Proxy handles secure connections without VPC configuration
Public IP + authorized networks for practice (never production)
--update-secrets mounts Secret Manager values as env vars (not --set-env-vars)
Runtime SA needs cloudsql.client + secretmanager.secretAccessor
Connection name format: PROJECT_ID:REGION:INSTANCE_NAME
@functions_framework.cloud_event decorator for Pub/Sub triggers

